title: Tesla Press Release Predicts Sales Decline
description:
Tesla has put out a press release warning its deliveries of new cars will be lower in the fourth quarter and for the year than expected.

The post Tesla Press Release Predicts Sales Decline appeared first on CleanTechnica.
